{"id": "1506220203518988288", "channel_id": "1503683160452501614", "type": 19, "author_id": "664488624242294826", "author_name": "max_architrator", "author_bot": false, "content": "Make sure she can summon us back to her, and give us a world of our own.", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T09:01:20.737000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["698796034016542720"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1503797766655180962", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1503683160452501614", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1 全新唤醒体✦沙耶┊New Awakener✦Saya", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1506233736356692001", "channel_id": "1503683160452501614", "type": 0, "author_id": "664488624242294826", "author_name": "max_architrator", "author_bot": false, "content": "The point around Saya small figure, her innocent look and suggested purity is to contrast her other appearance at best.\n\nHer personality is a lot like a kid playing around at all times, it's essential to get that her look is casual, like you'd see at the playground or the beach etc..\n\nIt is useless to make controversy about her fashion if the collaboration must respect the original product, and even in the  original as the story goes on it only takes away layers of her portrayed innocence (which is in tune with her character growth)\n\nThe base version they got illustrated for the game can call back to her first appearance but also to her ultimate transformation stimulated by ....\nI'm telling you if you don't consider this character special in nature and start considering it human you'll be in a tough spot reading the VN connecting things that are not and should not for the sake of human decency.\n\nIf Morimen game developers won't go into the cruder aspects of Saya they still wouldn't create a version of their own which overdresses her or shows the flesh parallel version, which has been intended for you to wonder about.\n\nIf it was an independent design no one would've been saying anything, but since this is an official collaboration, working against the original art wouldn't make sense, as through this collaboration it is intended for Morimen players to come check out discover or re-discover the original VN unveiling everything about the character, and I assure you the base version of Saya with the light dress is far enough from the purity and restraint you expect this character to have at first look.\n\n\n+ Art is art y'all are free to leave notes about character designs when visiting the louvre museum in Paris.", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T09:55:07.217000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1503683160452501614", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1 全新唤醒体✦沙耶┊New Awakener✦Saya", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
